                                                          <\/div>\n\n                                                \n                                                <div class=\"vip-mega-panel vip-mega-card\">\n                                                                                                        <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                        href=\"\/es\/prestamo\/prestamo-de-inversion\">\n                                                        Pr\u00e9stamo de inversi\u00f3n\n                                                    <\/a>\n                                                                                                        <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                        href=\"\/es\/prestamo\/tarjeta-de-credito\">\n                                                        Tarjeta de cr\u00e9dito\n                                                    <\/a>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                                \n                                        <div\n                                            class=\"tab-pane fade \"\n                                            id=\"vip-pane-3\"\n                                            role=\"tabpanel\"\n                                            aria-labelledby=\"vip-tab-3\"\n                                            tabindex=\"0\">\n\n                                            <div class=\"vip-mega-grid\">\n                                                \n                                                <div class=\"vip-mega-panel vip-mega-card\">\n                                                                                                        <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                        href=\"\/es\/hipoteca\/programa-de-compra-llave-en-mano\">\n                                                        Programa de compra llave en mano\n                                                    <\/a>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n\n                                                \n                                                <div class=\"vip-mega-panel vip-mega-card\">\n                                                                                                        <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                        href=\"\/es\/hipoteca\/hipoteca\">\n                                                        Hipoteca\n                                                    <\/a>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                            <\/div>\n                                <\/div>\n\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/li>\n\n                <!-- Liens normaux -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/es\/construction\">Nuestro Equipo<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/es\/carrieres\">Carreras<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/es\/partenaires\">Socios<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/es\/contact\">Contacto<\/a><\/li>\n\n                <!-- CTA -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item ms-xl-2 my-3 my-xl-0\">\n                    <a href=\"\/es\/contact\" class=\"btn vip-btn-gold rounded-pill px-4 py-2 w-100 w-xl-auto\">\n                        Consulta gratuita\n                    <\/a>\n                <\/li>\n\n                <!-- Mobile: lien Services simple -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item d-xl-none\">\n                    <a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/es\/services\">Servicios<\/a>\n                <\/li>\n\n            <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/nav>\r\n    \r\n    \n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-white\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0\">\n                <h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">\u00bfQu\u00e9 es un seguro de vida?<\/h2>\n                <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 3px; background: var(--secondary-color); margin-bottom: 20px;\"><\/div>\n                <div class=\"text-muted text-justify\" style=\"line-height: 1.8;\">\n                    <p>El seguro de vida es un contrato entre un asegurado y un asegurador derivado de un proceso de evaluaci\u00f3n. En el marco de este contrato, el asegurador se compromete a pagar al beneficiario designado una cierta cantidad de dinero a cambio del pago regular de primas.<br><br>Esta cantidad de dinero, llamada beneficio por fallecimiento o capital por fallecimiento, generalmente est\u00e1 libre de impuestos para el beneficiario. Existen dos tipos principales de seguros: <strong>temporal<\/strong> y <strong>permanente<\/strong>.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/A-cote-texte-assurance-vie-1.jpg\" alt=\"\u00bfQu\u00e9 es un seguro de vida?\" class=\"img-fluid rounded shadow-lg\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding pb-0\" style=\"background-color: #f8f9fa;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-5\">\n            <h3 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">1. Seguro de vida Temporal<\/h3>\n            <p class=\"text-muted\">Una soluci\u00f3n flexible para necesidades de duraci\u00f3n determinada.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<section class=\"py-5 mb-5 d-flex align-items-center\" style=\"background-color: #0b0d26; width: 100%; border-radius: 0 200px 200px 0; min-height: 400px;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row g-4\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Protection-du-revenu.png\" alt=\"Duraci\u00f3n Limitada\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Duraci\u00f3n Limitada<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">El seguro de vida temporal ofrece una cobertura por un per\u00edodo definido, que va de 10 a 40 a\u00f1os.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Paiement-des-dettes.png\" alt=\"Renovable\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Renovable<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Al final del per\u00edodo de cobertura, el contrato puede renovarse, a menudo con primas m\u00e1s altas.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Securite-financiere.png\" alt=\"Convertible\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Convertible<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">El seguro temporal puede convertirse en una p\u00f3liza de seguro de vida permanente sin necesidad de un examen m\u00e9dico.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding pb-0\" style=\"background-color: #f8f9fa;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-5\">\n            <h3 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">2. Seguro de vida Permanente<\/h3>\n            <p class=\"text-muted\">Una protecci\u00f3n de por vida con beneficios financieros.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<section class=\"py-5 mb-5 d-flex align-items-center\" style=\"background-color: #0b0d26; width: 100%; border-radius: 200px 0 0 200px; min-height: 400px;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row g-4\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Protection-du-revenu.png\" alt=\"Duraci\u00f3n Indefinida\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Duraci\u00f3n Indefinida<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">El seguro de vida permanente proporciona cobertura durante toda la vida del asegurado.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Paiement-des-dettes.png\" alt=\"Valor de Rescate\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Valor de Rescate<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Puede pedir prestado contra el valor acumulado en la p\u00f3liza o retirarlo.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Securite-financiere.png\" alt=\"Inversi\u00f3n\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Inversi\u00f3n<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Algunas p\u00f3lizas incluyen componentes de inversi\u00f3n y dividendos.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-primary\" style=\"background-color: var(--primary) !important;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-5\">\n            <h2 class=\"fw-bold text-white\">Opciones de Suscripci\u00f3n<\/h2>\n            <p class=\"text-white-50\">Comprender la diferencia entre el seguro con y sin examen m\u00e9dico.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"row g-4\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 rounded h-100 bg-white shadow-lg border-0 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"d-flex align-items-center mb-3\">\n                 